      <title>博客主页文章内容折叠</title>
      <link href="/2023/12/27/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%B5%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0/"/>
      <url>/2023/12/27/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%B5%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%8A%98%E5%8F%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>问题</strong>：Hexo博客主页默认展示文章全部内容<br>如下图所示：</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/12/27/AZFvplLEdRegMqu.png"><br>然而这样影响查找文章的效率且不美观，所以主页文章目录仅展示文章部分内容，其余内容折叠起来最好。</p><p><strong>解决</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>方法一：在文章要折叠的内容之前添加如下代码：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/12/27/1AzxMnImV8RwKP5.png"></p></li><li><p>方法二：修改当前主题下的文章模板，实现自动添加 Read More 标记<br>打开 <code>themes/landscape/layout/_partial/article.ejs</code> 文件（该路径与所用主题有关），找到与摘要相关的代码，修改为：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div class=&quot;article-entry&quot; itemprop=&quot;articleBody&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;% if (post.excerpt &amp;&amp; index) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;%- post.excerpt %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% if (theme.excerpt_link) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;p class=&quot;article-more-link&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;a href=&quot;&lt;%- config.root %&gt;&lt;%- post.path %&gt;#more&quot;&gt;&lt;%= theme.excerpt_link %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;% &#125; else &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% var br = post.content.indexOf(&#x27;\n&#x27;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% if(br &lt; 0 || !index) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;%- post.content %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; else &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;%- post.content.substring(0, br) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;% if (theme.excerpt_link) &#123; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;p class=&quot;article-more-link&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">          &lt;a href=&quot;&lt;%- config.root %&gt;&lt;%- post.path %&gt;#more&quot;&gt;&lt;%= theme.excerpt_link %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;% &#125; %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>则在文章没有 more 标记的时候，截取文章的前两段作为摘要，如果文章少于两段，直接显示整篇文章内容<br>注意：文章前两段不要包含代码片段。</p></li></ul><p><strong>效果</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>方法一：<br><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/12/27/ZkqDBrtKsfo7AgF.png"></p></li><li><p>方法二：<img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/12/27/IKwF2YpZMEtOlA7.png"></p></li></ul><p><strong>引用</strong>：</p><ul><li><a href="https://strongrock.github.io/2018-11-15/hexo%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/">方法一：Hexo首页不显示文章全部内容的设置方法</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/itguangzhi/article/details/79510044">方法二：Hexo博客首页自动添加Read More标记</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
      
